snippet.title: Muddledash - Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
PQube and slampunks are thrilled to reveal that the ultimate competitive party game, Muddledash, will be arriving on Nintendo Switch and PC/Steam July 10th, 2018! The game will launch on Nintendo Switch at the price of £4.79/$5.39/€4.99 with a pre-order available on June 12th at 14:00 BST/15:00 CEST offering 10% OFF!

The title will also launch on PC via Steam at the price of £4.79/$5.99/€4.99 with a 10% Launch Discount available for the first week of purchase from July 10th!

Come chat to us on our PQube Discord server! https://discord.gg/xHS7MnU
